Professional Takeoff Services

Accurate AGTEK Quantities for Winning Bids

Quantity Takeoffs

Professional AGTEK Takeoff Services

Get accurate earthwork quantities and material calculations using industry-leading AGTEK software. We deliver detailed takeoffs that help you bid confidently, win more work, and avoid costly surprises.

What We Calculate:

  • Cut/fill volumes and mass haul analysis
  • Topsoil stripping and re-spread quantities
  • Rock excavation and unsuitable material volumes
  • Asphalt tonnage and concrete volumes
  • Aggregate base and subbase quantities
  • Underground utility trench and backfill volumes
  • Pipe lengths and fitting counts
  • Surface areas for all material types
  • Phased construction breakdowns

Who It's For:

  • General contractors bidding site work projects
  • Excavation contractors needing accurate earthwork quantities
  • Paving contractors calculating material requirements
  • Utility contractors pricing underground work
  • Estimators with tight bid deadlines

Service Details:

Turnaround Time

24-48 hours for most projects

Software

AGTEK Earthwork 4D (industry standard)

Deliverables

Detailed reports with visual documentation

Support

Direct access to takeoff specialists

Fast turnaround â€¢ Competitive pricing

Why Accurate Takeoffs Matter

Every bid depends on accurate quantities. Underestimate and you lose money on the job. Overestimate and you lose the bid to your competition. Our AGTEK takeoffs give you the precision you need to bid right and win profitable work.

We've completed hundreds of takeoffs for contractors across the country. Our thorough approach catches details others miss, while our fast turnaround ensures you never miss a bid deadline. When accuracy matters, contractors trust AB Civil.

Need It Now?

Rush service available for tight deadlines.

Questions About Takeoffs?

Talk directly with our takeoff team.
